PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION unto Her Majesty whereby the BURRARD BAND OF INDIANS (Tsleil'waututh Nation) surrenders, for a term of 109 years, some 4.05 hectares (10 acres) of land (Lots 79-2 and 79-4, C.L.S.R.
